OL,3,CBlue whales are losing their voices,
OL,4,Cbut what is causing the silence?
OL,6,FThe study, published in PLOS (Public
OL,7,FLibrary of Science), found that marine
OL,8,Fheatwaves were affecting blue whales'
OL,9,Fprimary food source, krill. When krill
OL,10,Fpopulations fell, blue whale
OL,11,Fvocalisations became less and less
OL,12,Fprevalent.
OL,14,FIt's a stark reminder that climate
OL,15,Fchange can affect all living
OL,16,Fcreatures, big and small.
