OL,3,CBlue whales are losing their voices,
OL,4,Cbut what is causing the silence?
OL,6,FThe whales were recorded off the coast
OL,7,Fof California using a hydrophone - a
OL,8,Fmicrophone placed on the ocean floor,
OL,9,Ffrom July 2015 to June 2021.
OL,11,FThe researchers analysed the songs of
OL,12,Fthree types of whale: blue, fin and
OL,13,Fhumpback, which, according to the US
OL,14,FNational Oceanic and Atmospheric
OL,15,FAdministration, make noise to
OL,16,Fcommunicate, find food and for
OL,17,Fnavigation.
