OL,3,CBlue whales are losing their voices,
OL,4,Cbut what is causing the silence?
OL,6,FNotably, humpback whales feed on a
OL,7,Fvariety of species, from krill to
OL,8,Fsmall schools of fish like anchovies.
OL,9,FBlue whales, however, almost solely
OL,10,Ffeed on krill.
OL,12,FAccording to the study, during the
OL,13,Ffirst three years, the abundance of
OL,14,Fforage fish like anchovies and
OL,15,Fsardines was persistently low, while
OL,16,Fkrill stocks steadily increased. All
OL,17,Fthree whale species' song detection
OL,18,Fincreased during these three years.
