OL,3,CBlue whales are losing their voices,
OL,4,Cbut what is causing the silence?
OL,6,FIn the latter three years of the
OL,7,Fstudy, a marine heatwave that had been
OL,8,Faffecting the region began to impact
OL,9,Fthe abundance of krill.
OL,11,FSuddenly, an abundant food source
OL,12,Fbecame scarce, and blue whale song
OL,13,Fbegan to be heard less and less,
OL,14,Fdecreasing by approximately 40%.
