OL,3,CBlue whales are losing their voices,
OL,4,Cbut what is causing the silence?
OL,6,FIn contrast, school fish stocks
OL,7,Fincreased, particularly sardines.
OL,8,FScientists were able to suspect the
OL,9,Flack of blue whale song was due to a
OL,10,Flack of available food, because
OL,11,Fhumpback song detection increased, as
OL,12,Fthey ate varieties of fish in addition
OL,13,Fto krill.
OL,15,FThe marine heatwave had a name: "the
OL,16,FBlob". It began in 2013 in the Bering
OL,17,FSea and Gulf of Alaska, before
OL,18,Fexpanding and spreading across the
OL,19,FPacific Ocean.
