OL,3,CBlue whales are losing their voices,
OL,4,Cbut what is causing the silence?
OL,6,F"They're spending all their energy
OL,7,Fsearching. There's just not enough
OL,8,Ftime left over`and that tells us those
OL,9,Fyears are incredibly stressful.
OL,11,F"When you really break it down, it's
OL,12,Flike trying to sing while you're
OL,13,Fstarving...
OL,15,F"They were spending all their time
OL,16,Fjust trying to find food."
OL,18,FEarth recorded its hottest year ever
OL,19,Fin 2024, and global average
OL,20,Ftemperatures exceeded 1.5C for the
OL,21,Ffirst time.
