OL,3,CBlue whales are losing their voices,
OL,4,Cbut what is causing the silence?
OL,6,FThe oceans store about 91% of the
OL,7,Fworld's excess heat, driving
OL,8,Fdetrimental changes in every component
OL,9,Fof the climate system, including sea
OL,10,Flevel rise, ocean warming, ice loss,
OL,11,Fand permafrost thawing.
OL,13,FUN scientists have said that the Earth
OL,14,Fis running out of time to prevent
OL,15,Fglobal warming from breaching 1.5C on
OL,16,Faverage.
