OL,6,FThey say that without drastic cuts to
OL,7,Femissions, the world will be unable to
OL,8,Fprevent warming from surpassing the
OL,9,Fdangerous threshold, which will lead
OL,10,Fto a rise in extreme weather events,
OL,11,Fclimate-related disasters and increase
OL,12,Fthe risk of triggering irreversible
OL,13,Fchanges.
OL,15,FAmong those terrifying outcomes, the
OL,16,Feerie silence of the ocean's largest
OL,17,Fcreature.
